notes: Map AGE_TYPE metadata to the notation concept and represent concrete codes in codes.csv.
Use ConfidenceCategory as current canonical reuse point for quality ratings pending a dedicated index-quality scheme.
REFERENCE fields are bibliographic metadata and should remain attribute role, not measurement.
Reuse canonical benchmark class for lower/WSP lower benchmark fields.
Reuse canonical benchmark class for upper/WSP upper benchmark fields.
Use existing management stratum class for upper/lower management level metadata fields.
Reuse canonical HatcheryOrigin concept (SalmonOriginScheme) as origin qualifier.
Use Darwin Core individualCount for unresolved count-like terms where no domain-specific class exists yet.
Treat terminal run size as count pending a dedicated run-size concept in GCDFO.
Use TotalExploitationRate where field definition indicates fishery-caused mortality proportion.
